text: The first season of I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here premiered on Network Ten on 1 February 2015. The season was hosted by Julia Morris and Chris Brown. Andrew 'Freddie' Flintoff won the season, getting crowned King of the Jungle on 15 March 2015. == References == Category:I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! Category:2010s television seasons
title: I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! (Australian season 1)
